<div id="bsod-menu" class="bsod-screen" style="display: none;">
  <div class="crt">
    <div class="crt-screen">
      <div class="bsod-content">
        <!-- Authentic Windows XP BSOD Header -->
        <div class="bsod-header">
          <p>A problem has been detected and Windows has been shut down to prevent damage</p>
          <p>to your computer.</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>PORTFOLIO_NAVIGATION_FAULT</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>If this is the first time you've seen this Stop error screen,</p>
          <p>restart your computer. If this screen appears again, follow</p>
          <p>these steps:</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>Check to make sure any new hardware or software is properly installed.</p>
          <p>If this is a new installation, ask your hardware or software manufacturer</p>
          <p>for any Windows updates you might need.</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>If problems continue, disable or remove any newly installed hardware</p>
          <p>or software. Disable BIOS memory options such as caching or shadowing.</p>
          <p>If you need to use Safe Mode to remove or disable components, restart</p>
          <p>your computer, press F8 to select Advanced Startup Options, and then</p>
          <p>select Safe Mode.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Technical Information -->
        <div class="bsod-technical">
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>Technical information:</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>*** STOP: 0x0000007E (0xC0000005, 0xF7A3B2C1, 0xF8A4D3E8, 0xF8A4D0E4)</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>***  portfolio.sys - Address F7A3B2C1 base at F7A30000, DateStamp 4a5bc600</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Navigation Menu Section -->
        <div class="bsod-separator">
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>===================================================================================</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>NAVIGATION OPTIONS - SELECT TO CONTINUE:</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
        </div>

        <nav class="menu" role="navigation" aria-label="Main menu">
          <div class="menu-item" data-target="about" tabindex="0">
            <span class="menu-arrow">►</span> [0x01] ABOUT - System Information and Biography
          </div>
          <div class="menu-item" data-target="skills" tabindex="0">
            <span class="menu-arrow">►</span> [0x02] SKILLS - Technical Capabilities and Stack Trace
          </div>
          <div class="menu-item" data-target="blog" tabindex="0">
            <span class="menu-arrow">►</span> [0x03] BLOG - Memory Dump and Articles
          </div>
          <div class="menu-item" data-target="contact" tabindex="0">
            <span class="menu-arrow">►</span> [0x04] CONTACT - Establish Network Connection
          </div>
        </nav>

        <!-- Footer Section -->
        <div class="bsod-footer">
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>===================================================================================</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p>Beginning dump of physical memory</p>
          <p>Physical memory dump complete.</p>
          <p>Contact your system administrator or technical support group for further assistance.</p>
          <p>&nbsp;</p>
          <p class="help-text">KEYBOARD: ↑↓ arrows to navigate • ENTER to select • ESC to close modal</p>
          <p class="help-text">MOUSE: Click any option to proceed</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .bsod-screen {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--bsod-blue);
    z-index: 100;
    opacity: 0;
    animation: fade-in 0.1s steps(2, jump-start) forwards;
  }

  @keyframes fade-in {
    to {
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  .bsod-content {
    padding: 30px;
    padding-left: 40px;
    /* LEFT-ALIGNED like authentic Windows XP BSOD */
    text-align: left;
    max-width: none;
    height: 100vh;
    overflow-y: auto;
  }

  .bsod-header p,
  .bsod-technical p,
  .bsod-separator p,
  .bsod-footer p {
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .bsod-header {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .bsod-technical {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .bsod-separator {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .menu {
    margin: 0;
  }

  .menu-item {
    padding: 4px 0;
    margin: 2px 0;
    cursor: pointer;
    position: relative;
    outline: none;
    display: block;
  }

  .menu-item:hover,
  .menu-item:focus,
  .menu-item.selected {
    background: var(--bsod-text);
    color: var(--bsod-blue);
  }

  .menu-arrow {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 15px;
    margin-right: 5px;
  }

  .menu-item:not(.selected) .menu-arrow {
    opacity: 0;
  }

  .menu-item.selected .menu-arrow {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .bsod-footer {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  .help-text {
    color: var(--bsod-gray);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .bsod-content {
      padding: 15px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .menu-item {
      padding: 8px 4px;
      touch-action: manipulation;
    }

    .help-text {
      font-size: 11px;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .bsod-content {
      padding: 10px;
      padding-left: 15px;
      font-size: 11px;
    }

    .help-text {
      font-size: 10px;
    }
  }
</style>

<script src="../scripts/menu.ts"></script>
